      "last_updated": "2026-04-28",
      "status": "current",
      "_note_2026_04_28": "Catalog correctness pass: fixed Qwen3 native contexts (32K not 40K/256K), Devstral native (256K not 384K), renamed Gemma 4 27B (nonexistent) to Gemma 4 26B-A4B; added Qwen3-14B, Qwen3-30B-A3B-Instruct-2507, Qwen3-4B-Instruct-2507, Granite 4.0 H-Micro/H-Tiny/H-Small. Per code review: all entries with unverified Ollama tags carry internal=True (filtered from user picker until tags are verified against ollama.com/library) — user-pickable list is the 6 original entries with verified tags, internal universe is 7 entries reserved for the future InferenceRouter (ADR 004). Each internal entry carries a TODO: verify Ollama tag comment. Tool_mode taxonomy renamed: native→native_qwen3, json_fallback→adapted, limited→excluded_from_tools (per ADR 004 'Tool-format hardening'). Added probe_runtime_load() + GET /api/local/runtime/load — pure-Python scaffold for the dispatcher's runtime-load signal (psutil + Ollama /api/ps); macOS branch graduates to Tauri-native after ADR 003. Catalog gained ADR-004 fields: bytes_per_kv_token / attention_arch (transformer|mamba|swa) / slot_class (consumed by InferenceRouter for footprint accounting and slot lookup). Per-slot keep_alive policy table (KEEP_ALIVE_BY_SLOT) replaces the hard-coded '30m'; warm_up_model() reads the policy via the catalog entry's slot_class so plumbing/embedding stay forever-resident, on-demand slots evict in 5m."
    },
    "inference-router": {
      "doc": "docs/features/inference-router.md",
      "type": "feature",
